window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gamblers and goblins. Dragons and duels. Scoundrels of every make and description.</p> <p>Dive back into the worlds of the best-selling Twinborn Trilogy with this collection of eight short stories - including three exclusive, never-before-published works. J.S. Morin peels back the larger Twinborn story to reveal the smaller tales concealed beneath.</p> <p>Gamble with pirates in \"Crackle Man\". Curry favor with a living god in \"To Serve a Dragon\". Join the hunt for ogres in \"War-Bringer\".&nbsp;</p> <p>For some characters, this is their beginning. For others, this is the end. But for a fortunate few, their adventures continue on in <i>Twinborn Chronicles: War of 3 Worlds</i>.</p>"; 
